<BaseLayout title="About — s_0 studio">
<section>
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    S_0 refers to a point of origin — where each project is defined before it is developed.
    Projects are resolved through plan, proportion, and material.
Spatial layout establishes the logic. Materials are specified with precision. Details are defined prior to execution.
  </p>
</section>



  <!-- Founder -->
  <div class="team-founder">
    <figure>
      <img src="/images/Andi Dumitru2.jpg" alt="Founder portrait" />
      <figcaption>
        <strong> arch. Andi Dumitru</strong><br />
        Founder / Architect
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <p class="founder-bio">
      Fully licensed architect, with studies in the UK and Milan at leading universities, and
      extensive professional experience across Romania, the United Kingdom,
      and Italy. Has worked with award-winning practices on projects spanning
      multiple scales and typologies.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p>
   The studio works with a limited number of projects at a time. Each project is developed with direct involvement, controlled timelines, and clear documentation. 
   We work alongside a trusted network of constructors, manufacturers, and suppliers — ensuring consistency between concept, detail, and execution.
   Every project is carried through with precision, from first line to final build.
  </p>

</section>
  <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">
    Start a project
  </a>
</section>

</section>
</BaseLayout>
